---
// Slide 9: Benefits for Students (4 Benefit Cards)
---

<div class="slide-frame inactive w-full" id="slide-9" data-slide="8">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
    <!-- Left Column: Header -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-4">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold text-neonIndigo uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
        09 // Student Growth
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-outfit text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        Benefit<br />Untuk Siswa
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        Ekosistem yang memberdayakan perkembangan diri siswa secara
        progresif untuk menyambut standar karier masa depan mereka.
      </p>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-cardDark/50 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <span class="text-white font-bold block mb-1">Motto Program:</span>
        Siswa tidak hanya belajar teori pasif, tetapi benar-benar
        bekerja secara kolaboratif dalam ekosistem industri modern yang
        lincah.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: 4 Benefit Cards -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <!-- Card 1: Pengalaman Nyata -->
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-lime">
        <div class="text-neonLime text-lg mb-2">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-base font-bold text-white mb-1">
          Pengalaman Nyata
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Pengalaman kerja nyata berbasis proyek industri dengan
          tantangan nyata.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Portofolio Profesional -->
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-indigo">
        <div class="text-neonIndigo text-lg mb-2">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-base font-bold text-white mb-1">
          Portofolio Profesional
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Membangun portofolio industri bersertifikasi resmi yang diakui
          klien.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Mastery Pitching -->
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-lime">
        <div class="text-neonLime text-lg mb-2">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-base font-bold text-white mb-1">
          Mastery Pitching
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Melatih kemampuan pitching, komunikasi bisnis &amp; presentasi
          standar agensi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Problem Solving -->
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-cardDark border border-white/5 hover-lift glow-coral">
        <div class="text-neonCoral text-lg mb-2">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-outfit text-base font-bold text-white mb-1">
          Problem Solving
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Mengasah insting adaptabilitas dalam memecahkan masalah
          industri kreatif.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
